\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
y^{\Omega}=\ln\left(1-r\right)\label{eq:boundary}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

; thus, the end of an epidemic corresponds to the rightmost intersection
 
\begin_inset Formula $P^{\infty}$
\end_inset

 of eq.
