\end_inset

 the whole orthant 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{0}<\boldsymbol{s}<\boldsymbol{1}$
\end_inset

.
 For such sets, we have that 
\begin_inset Formula $\chi_{A}<\chi_{B}\to\Phi^{\chi_{A}}\subset\Phi^{\chi_{B}}$
\end_inset

; also, the number of 
